360
00:23:32,828 --> 00:23:33,828
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

361
00:23:34,999 --> 00:23:36,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf tidaklah cukup.</font>

362
00:23:36,368 --> 00:23:39,769
<font color=#FFFF00>Tindakan gilamu itu hampir menghancurkan perusahaan kita!</font>

363
00:23:39,999 --> 00:23:41,668
