364
00:23:41,999 --> 00:23:45,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Man Ho. To--tolong hentikan.</font>

365
00:23:47,578 --> 00:23:49,408
<font color=#FFFF00>Te--tenanglah, Man Ho.</font>

366
00:23:53,148 --> 00:23:54,818
<font color=#FFFF00>Ajeossi akan bagaimana?</font>

367
00:23:55,989 --> 00:23:58,418
