369
00:23:59,858 --> 00:24:01,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu itu?</font>

370
00:24:01,118 --> 00:24:02,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, aku?</font>

371
00:24:04,689 --> 00:24:07,658
